Revision history for Tk::TextANSIColor

0.17 2024-07-05

  - Attempt to use current font for bold text, to avoid it being
    displayed in a different size.  (CPAN bug: #125702)

  - Allow "\e[m" as an alternative reset sequence. (CPAN bug: #125702)

0.16 2010-12-03

  - Fix CPAN Testers failure with no X display.

  - Use Module::Build and Test::More.

0.15 2003-08-18

  - Tweak the way that fonts are specified in TextANSIColor
    such that the Tk::Font system is used.

0.14 2001-10-20

  - Add getansi() method from Jim Turner <turnerjw2@netscape.net>
    and related test. This allows the ANSI escape codes to be retrieved
    from the Text widget.

0.13 2001-01-02

  - Include Tk::ROTextANSIColor in the MANIFEST.

0.12 2000-11-24

  - Add Read-only widget Tk::ROTextANSIColor at request of
    Piotr Synowiec <mysiar@krakow.sky.pl>.

0.11 2000-05-02

  - Add proper test routine.

0.10 1999-05-18

  - Initial release.
